{"tid":164213,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【中韓反目】樂天摺埋中國20分店 每月損失逾8億元","createTime":"2017-03-20T13:46:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-21T06:58:12.000Z","uid":22675,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d1479bb5c042e4f14f46528cd41f70c2f6080f79","tid":164213,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T13:46:58.000Z","msg":"2017年03月20日<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170320/large/1490012587_5844.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170320%2Flarge%2F1490012587_5844.jpg&h=21969668&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n南韓傳媒報道，讓出高爾夫球場部署「薩德」反導系統的南韓樂天集團，因被中國制抵，該集團主動關閉中國境內約20間門店。早前，內地67間樂天商場，各因消防整頓而被勒令停業。<br />\n<br />\n南韓KBS電視台的報道指，目前樂天集團在華擁有99間大型商場，67間樂天商場因為消防安全問題而被要求暫停營業整頓，樂天集團又主動關閉了另外20家商場，這意味着超過90%樂天在華商場不再營業。<br />\n報道稱，樂天集團將為此付出每月1,160億韓圜（8.06億港元）的損失，而停止營業期間還必須繼續支付僱員工資。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20170320/56455962\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20170320%2F56455962&d=FZDcFY5BXo0CBgddFpFX554%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=71a841f8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20170320%2F56455962&h=79578615\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20170320/56455962</a>"},{"pid":"a6e8d7c4a1aa2e650d642252fc1269e6d6673a11","tid":164213,"uid":14282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T13:56:46.000Z","msg":"一年係中國咪成百億港紙純收入？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真唔真呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57e32e1f4edb9cee3d76817c0329710c6ad7f9ee","tid":164213,"uid":5715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T14:00:12.000Z","msg":"我就唔信<img src=\"/assets/face